	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">Our Fall Colours</h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶God, it‚Äôs a hellhole in here, Sven from Vogue almost has his camera down Vanessa‚Äôs cleavage ‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶ such a crush, what‚Äôs Mario done, sold his soul? Last year was all D-list celebs and promo people, this year there‚Äôs a real buzz‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶ heard it‚Äôs something special, he‚Äôs doing things with colour that aren‚Äôt ¬†technically possible ‚Äì it‚Äôs not shot silk, those scarves change colour even when they‚Äôre not moving‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶did you see her walking? She‚Äôs chalk-white and has lost about twenty pounds. I bet it‚Äôs heroin‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶who‚Äôs smoking in here, anyway? Bloody ash everywhere‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶no, it‚Äôs not blue, not quite. Never seen anything like it. That ballgown‚Äôs fierce, the colour‚Äôs otherworldly and the drape‚Äôs frankly impossible‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶apparently she never goes anywhere without wearing something in the new fabric, quite an obsession‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶God, darling, have a canape, you look like you‚Äôre about to pass out‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶no idea of the technology, he‚Äôs keeping it very quiet, says his science team is a bit out of the box and doesn‚Äôt want publicity‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶ bold new experiments with texture and hue, these fabrics defy categorisation ‚Äì hell, Paul, get the camera on <em>me, </em>for fuck‚Äôs sake‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶like an epidemic, models dropping like flies, even more than usual. ¬†That new fabric isn‚Äôt healthy‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶ saw her after the show, nearly collapsing, ash everywhere ‚Äì when did she start chain-smoking? That weird almost-blue shade makes her look dead, frankly‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶ Mario, darling, huge triumph, really edgy clothes‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶ no, I tell you, it‚Äôs aliens! Lovecraft was right! Aliens are infiltrating our fashion! That fabric‚Äôs alive! You laugh now ‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
<p>‚Äú‚Ä¶ God, did you hear? Annabel‚Äôs dead‚Ä¶‚Äù</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	
	<footer class="entry-footer">
