				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Development team would be better, definitely. Any mention of &#8220;science&#8221; gives me V flashbacks (completely appropriate here, actually.)</p>
<p>I meant to say one more thing &#8211; when playing with dialogue snippets, consider using fragments rather than full sentences &#8211; it&#8217;s not how people write, but it&#8217;s often how they talk. E.g. &#8220;She‚Äôs chalk-white and has lost about twenty pounds&#8221; vs &#8220;Chalk-white and lost about twenty pounds.&#8221; iyswim. <img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>
